data.description: Price reduced! Magical cottage charmer featuring ocean views on both levels! Original 1938 build with tasteful 1994 expansion in pristine condition, featuring two bedrooms, two baths, finished basement and detached oversized two car garage. Convenient to nearby beach accesses, dining, shops, and other amenities. Roof replaced three years ago.
